RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

96-2085. Grove v. Tracy.

Board of Tax Appeals, Nos. 95-K-264 and 95-K-265. Reported at 77 Ohio St.3d 1459, 672 N.E.2d 182.

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration of the dismissal of the appeal for want of prosecution be, and hereby is, denied.
